      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are currently functional, though the car shows signs of age with some minor fluid leaks and a suspension that feels a bit soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear and staining. While it passed its last inspection, it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for transportation at a reasonable price point.",
