    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, she\u2019s in such incredible shape it feels like she just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car\u2014it\u2019s been totally babied, garage-kept, and is looking absolutely flawless. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
