    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an immaculate 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2), a definitive driver\u2019s specification featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. This example has undergone a comprehensive mechanical refresh: the IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with a LN Engineering ceramic retrofit, and the Rear Main Seal (RMS) is bone dry. The chassis dynamics are enhanced by a Bilstein B16 coilover suite, providing precise damping and optimized roll centers. Engine compression is within factory tolerances across all cylinders with no evidence of bore scoring. The naturally aspirated power delivery is linear and urgent, complemented by a factory-optioned limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 model. Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Single owner. Clean title. Inspection reports available.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
