    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! I am seriously in love with this ride, and it breaks my heart a little to let it go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it. It is in absolutely stunning, pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it was first bought! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a total gem that's been treated with a ton of love, you've found it! Feel free to shoot me any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat!",
