    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-quality condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual VANOS for a linear 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a GKN variable M-differential. The chassis remains structurally pristine, with the rear subframe mounting points showing zero fatigue. Performance is optimized via aluminum control arms and a 50/50 weight distribution, ensuring neutral handling and high-speed stability. The exterior finish and interior ergonomics are flawlessly preserved, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance.",
